metadata.name: Zombified #1
metadata.description: Zombified is a collection of 444 AI illustrated zombies based on the likenesses of famous celebrities, athletes and other public figures. The collection is a satirical take on large societal figures, billionaires, actors, as well as everyday individuals and how AI will begin to overrun society over the next few 100 years. In fact, this very description was made using AI. Welcome to the future, watch your back.
